openapi: 3.0.0
servers:

info:
  description: 'REST countries API'
  title: REST countries API
  version: v2.0.5

    get:
      operationId: v1All
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
        default:
          description: Other responses
  /v1/alpha/{alphacode}:
    get:
      operationId: v1Alphacode
      parameters:
        - name: alphacode
          description: Search by ISO 3166-1 2-letter or 3-letter country code
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
        default:
          description: Other responses

          description: Successful response
        default:

        default:
          description: Other responses
  /v1/name/{name}:
    get:
      operationId: v1Name

          description: Search by country name. It can be the native name or partial name
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: fullText
          description: Search by country full name
          in: query
          required: false
